GENERIC_1_DEF NewFeatureType   fme_type                     fme_any   VendorID                     int16   VendorName                   varchar(48)   VendorDescription            varchar(16)   OBJECTID                     int64   BookCount                    int32   CentreAddress                varchar(30)   CentreName                   varchar(30)   CentreURL                    varchar(50)   Circulation                  int32   Description                  varchar(75)   FountainID                   int16   LibraryAddress               varchar(30)   LibraryID                    varchar(6)   LibraryName                  varchar(30)   LibraryURL                   varchar(80)   Location                     varchar(50)   Maintainer                   varchar(16)   NumAddresses                 int16   ParkAddress                  varchar(50)   ParkName                     varchar(30)   ParkURL                      varchar(100)   Regulation                   varchar(75)   Schedule                     varchar(30)   StationName                  varchar(30)   Subzone                      varchar(30)   UserVisits                   int32   Zone                         varchar(30)
